channel.title: Anyone Need Help Paying for Premium?
channel.description: Hi guys any US users who can’t afford to get premium? Growing up without much money, I understand limitations especially with strict parents. Also when I had extreme anxiety as a 20 year old adult being active approx 2 hours a day and not being able to handle interaction- let alone work to maintain- I feel that. Music is a big, important, and meaningful way to express myself and i’m sure all of you resonate with that too. I’ll gift 3 people $6 each on the app store so you can subcribe to premium for a month. US just cuz you can’t gift internationally, unless ya’ll know how to do that as well :/
